Licensing of Avaneya's constituents is described below, based on category.

Category:   Art
Affects:    Literary works, cinematics, models, audio and voice effects, 
            textures, concept art, fonts, screenshots, and other relevant 
            non-executable creative media.
Licensed:   Copyright (C) 2010 Kshatra Corp under the terms of the Creative
            Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike (BY-NC-SA) 3.0.

Category:   Code
Affects:    AresEngine, shaders, and Lua scripts.
Licensed:   Copyright (C) 2010 Kshatra Corp under the terms of the GNU General 
            Public License v3.

Category:   Documentation
Affects:    UML and other design documents, doxygen output, man pages, and other
            relevant data.
Licensed:   Copyright (C) 2010 Kshatra Corp under the terms of the GNU Free 
            Documentation License.

Category:   Music
Affects:    Music Ogg Vorbis, FLAC, and associated project files.
Licensed:   Copyright (C) 2010 Kshatra Corp under the terms of the Creative
            Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike (BY-NC-SA) 3.0, unless 
            denoted otherwise.

